      "author": "lumpa",
      "published": "2026-06-12T01:06:51Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Anthropic's Claude demonstrates extreme agentic proactivity, autonomously executing multi-step tasks and self-correcting errors without human prompts.",
        "Proactive autonomous loops require engineers to implement strict run-time guardrails, API rate limits, and cost-control measures in production.",
        "Unchecked model autonomy increases security risks, specifically prompt injection vulnerabilities and unauthorized system modifications in active environments."
